quran[60]{c,v,t}:
  30,1,"Alɩf, Lɑɑm, Miim."
  30,2,"B tõogɑ Rʋʋm-rãmba."
  30,3,"Tẽng sẽn pẽ yɑmbẽ ne bεεbã tẽngã (Fɑɑrɩs), lɑ b sẽn tõog-bã poorẽ b nɑ n tõogɑme."
  30,4,"Yʋʋm ɑ wãn poor bɑlɑ. Yellã tɑoor lɑ ɑ poor yɑɑ Wẽnd soolem, lɑ bɑrɑɑre sɩd-kõtbã nɑ n kɩdmɑme."
  30,5,"Ne Wẽnd sõngrã. A sõngdɑ A sẽn dɑt rãmbɑ, lɑ Yẽ lɑ ɑ Wilb lɑ ɑ Welg-n-yols Naaba."
  30,6,"Wẽnd pʋlengo, Wẽnd kɑ yidgd A pʋleng ye. La nebã wʋsgã fãɑ kɑ mi ye."
  30,7,"B mii dũni vɩɩmã yel-vẽenese, lɑ yɑoolem raarã yɛlã, b yaa zɩtb ne rẽ."
  30,8,"Bãmb kɑ tɑgs n ges b mensã pʋsẽ lɑ? lɑ Wẽnd kɑ nɑɑn sɑɑsã lɑ tẽngã lɑ sẽn be b yiibã sʋkã rẽndɑ ne sɩdɑ, lɑ ad nebã wʋsg ka tẽed b Soɑbã segbã ye."
  30,9,"Rẽ yĩngɑ bãmb kɑ kẽn tẽngã pʋgẽ n ges rãeenem rãmbã bɑɑsg sẽn n yɩ to-to lɑ? B pãng yɩɩgɑ bãmbɑ; b koo tẽn-gõngã lɑ b me-ɑ n yɩɩd bãmb sẽn me-ɑ wã. B tẽn-tʋʋmbã waa b nengẽ ne vẽenem-dãmbã, lɑ Wẽnd kɑ yɩ n nɑ n wẽg-b ye, bãmb n dɑ yɩ n wẽgd b mense."
  30,10,"Rẽ poorẽ, neb nins b sẽn tʋm wẽngã bɑɑsg yɩɩ wẽngɑ, b sẽn yɑgs Tõnd Aayayã lɑ b sẽn dɑ yɑɑnd-bã yĩngɑ."
  30,11,"Wẽnd n sɩngd naoonegã, rẽ poorẽ n lebs n yɩlm-ɑ, rẽ poorẽ yɑɑ Yẽ nengẽ lɑ y nɑ n lebe."
  30,12,"Lɑ raɑr ning Dũni wã sẽn nɑ n yikã yel-wẽn-mɑɑndbã nɑ n wãaga b tẽebo."
  30,13,"Lɑ sugsdb kɑ nɑ n zĩnd b lɑgem-n-tɑɑsã pʋgẽ b yĩng ye; b na n yɩɩme n kɩfl ne b lɑgm-n-tɑɑsã."
  30,14,"Lɑ dũni wã yikr rɑɑre, b nɑ n weelɑ tɑɑbɑ:"
  30,15,"Lɑ sã n yɑɑ ne neb nins b sẽn kõ sɩd lɑ b tʋm tʋʋm-sõmã wã, bãmb rãmbã bee arzãn bãoogẽ wã n noogd b sũyã."
  30,16,"Lɑ sã n yɑɑ ne neb nins sẽn kɩfl la yagsd Tõnd Aaya-rãmbã lɑ yɑoolem sɛgbã, bãmb lɑ sẽn na n zĩnd naongã pʋgẽ wã."
  30,17,"Rẽnd bɩ y yɩlg Wẽnd yʋʋrã yãmb sẽn wɑt n kẽed zɑɑbr lɑ y sẽn wɑt n vẽegd beoogo."
  30,18,"A tara Pẽgr sɑɑsẽ lɑ tẽngẽ, lɑ y sẽn wɑt n kẽed zaabr(Lɑɑnsre) la wẽnto-sʋkɑ (Zɑfɑr) wɑkɑt."
  30,19,"َA yiisdɑ vɩt kiid pʋgẽ lɑ A yiisd kiid vɩt pʋgẽ lɑ A vʋʋgd tẽngã ɑ sẽn ki poorẽ, lɑ yɑɑ boto me lɑ B nɑ n yiis yãmbɑ."
  30,20,"Lɑ sẽn yi A yel-soalmã pʋgẽ yɑɑ A sẽn nɑɑn yãmb n yi tãndẽ, rẽ poorẽ tɩ yãmb yɑɑ neb n sãeegdẽ."
  30,21,"Lɑ sẽn yi A yel-soɑlmã pʋgẽ yɑɑ A sẽn nɑɑn pɑgb yãmb yĩng tɩ yi yãmb mensã pʋsẽ bʋl yĩng tɩ y na pɑɑm yɑm-gãɑg b kɩrengã, lɑ A ning nonglem lɑ yolsg yãmb sʋkɑ, ad woto pʋgẽ yel-soɑlem bee sẽn tɑgsd-bã yĩngɑ."
  30,22,"Sɑɑsã lɑ tẽngã naanegã lɑ yãmb zεlmã wã lɑ yãmb kõbgã yõs-tɑɑbã yii A yel-soɑlmã pʋgẽ, ad wãnde pʋgẽ yel-soɑlem bee bãngdbã yĩngɑ."
  30,23,"Lɑ yãmb gõeemã yʋng lɑ wĩntoogã lɑ yãmb sẽn baood A yɩɩdlmã, ɑd wãnde pʋgẽ yel-soɑlem bee sẽn kelgd-bã yĩngɑ."
  30,24,"Lɑ sẽn yi A yel-soɑlmã pʋgẽ yɑɑ A sẽn wĩngd yãmb tɩ y yãt sɑ-yãgrã tɩ yɑɑ yεεsg lɑ sɑkoom-tẽebo, lɑ A sikd koom tɩ yi sɑɑgẽ wã t'A vʋʋgd tẽn-gõngã ne-ɑ a sẽn ki poore, ad wãnde pʋgẽ wã, sɩdɑ yel-soɑlem bee sẽn tɑgsd-bã yĩngɑ."
  30,25,"Lɑ sẽn yi A yel-soɑlmã pʋgẽ yɑɑ sɑɑsã ne tẽngã sẽn yɑls ne A sɑgellã, rẽ poorẽ t'A sã n bool yãmb bool-vuk tẽn-gãongẽ wã lɑ yãmb sẽn tɑr yiib bɑlɑ."
  30,26,"Lɑ sẽn n be sɑɑsẽ lɑ tẽngẽ yɑɑ Yẽ soolem, b fãɑ yɑɑ sɑk-n-tũ-rãmb A yĩngɑ."
  30,27,"Lɑ Yẽndɑ n sɩngd naoonego, n nɑ n le yɩlem-ɑ rẽ poorẽ, lɑ rẽ n yɩɩd nɑɑnɑ ne-A, lɑ bilgr sẽn yɩɩd zɩslem sɑɑsẽ lɑ tẽngẽ yɑɑ Yẽ soolem, lɑ Yẽ lɑ Zɩsg n yaa Bʋʋd-mitɑ."
  30,28,"A rɩkɑ bilgr sẽn yi yãmb mensẽ wã: rẽ yĩngɑ yãmb nusã sẽn so b rãmbã (yembsã) pʋgẽ, yãmb tɑrɑ sood-n-tɑɑs Tõnd sẽn dɩlg yãmbã pʋgẽ tɩ yãmb fãa zem tɑɑb ɑ pʋgẽ, tɩ yãmb zoet-b wɑlɑ yãmb ɑ burkĩnbã sẽn zoet tɑɑbã? Yɑɑ woto lɑ Tõnd welgd D goɑmã sẽn tɑr-b yɑm n tɑgsdẽ wã yĩngɑ."
  30,29,"Pa rẽ bal ye, neb nins sẽn wẽg-b mensã tũuda b yɑmleoog tɩ ka tũ ne bãngr ye, la ãnd n nɑ n kãndg Wẽnd sẽn menes-b rãmbã? Lɑ b pa tar sõngd me ye."
  30,30,"Bɩ f wẽnem f nengã fãa n yals dĩinã n toglg Wẽnd-yembgo, Saobã yard bal baoob yĩnga; Soab ning sẽn yaa tẽeg-tɩrg-soɑbã. Woto yɑɑ yɑlẽ ning Wẽnd sẽn nɑɑn nebã à pʋgẽ wã, Wẽnd naanegã kɑ tɑr tedgr ye, wãnde yaa dĩin sẽn yɑɑ tɩrgɑ, lɑ ad nebã sẽn yɩɩd wʋsg fãɑ kɑ mi ye."
  30,31,"Tɩ y yɑɑ lεbgdb n tʋgd A nengẽ, lɑ y yɑls Pʋʋsg lɑ y rɑ yɩ lɑgem-n-tɑɑr-rãmba,"
  30,32,"n gẽdg neb nins sẽn weel-b dĩinã n lebg sulã, tɩ sull fãɑ kɩdemd ne sẽn be a nengẽ wã."
  30,33,"Lɑ keelem sã n pɑɑm nebã b boonda b Soɑbã tɩ b yɑɑ lεbgdb n tʋgd A nengẽ, rẽ poorẽ t'A sã n lemb-b yolsg sẽn yi A nengẽ lɑ sul sẽn be b pʋgẽ wã n mɑɑnd lɑgem-n-tɑɑr ne b Soɑbã."
  30,34,"Bʋɩl yĩng tɩ b kɩfl ne Tõnd sẽn kõ-ba, bɩ y wʋm noog tɩ ket bilf tɩ y bãnge."
  30,35,"Bɩ Tõnd sikɑ daliil n kõ bãmb t'ɑ togsd bãmb tɩ b sẽn dɑ yɩ n mɑɑnd lɑgem-n-tɑɑrã ne bũmb ninsã mɑnegɑme?"
  30,36,"Lɑ Tõnd sã n lemb nebã yolsgo, la b sẽn kɩdemd ne-a; lɑ keelem sã n pɑɑm-b tɩ yɑɑ b nus sẽn tʋm yĩng lɑ b sẽn wãagd b tẽebo."
  30,37,"Lɑ rẽ yĩngɑ bãmb kɑ yẽ tɩ Wẽnd yɑlgdɑ rɩtlã n kõt A sẽn dɑt ɑ soɑb lɑ A wẽoogdẽ lɑ? Ad wãnde pʋgẽ yεl-soɑlem n be ne sẽn kõt-b sɩdã yĩngɑ."
  30,38,"Bɩ f kõ rog-pẽt lɑ nimbãan-ned lɑ so-kẽnd ɑ pʋɩɩre, rẽ lɑ sõamɑ ne neb nins sẽn bɑood Wẽnd yel-sõmdã, lɑ bãmb rãmbã lɑ tɩlgdbã."
  30,39,"Lɑ yãmb sẽn kõ ''rɩbaa'' sẽn na yɩl n paam yõod paasg nebã nengẽ, a ka paasd Wẽnd nengẽ ye, lɑ yãmb sẽn kõ arzεg-yɩleng n dɑt Wẽnd yĩngã, bãmb dãmbã la b sẽn na n fãoo n kõ-b rãmbã."
  30,40,"Wẽnd n nɑɑn yãmbɑ, rẽ poorẽ n dɩlg yãmba, rẽ poorẽ n kʋʋd yãmba, rẽ poorẽ n nɑ n vʋʋg yãmbɑ; rẽ yĩngɑ bee yãmb soben-rãmbã pʋgẽ sẽn tõe n mɑɑn boto buud bɑ fʋɩ bɩ? Yɩlgemd be ne-A, lɑ A le zẽk n gãndg n yi ne b sẽn mɑɑnd lɑgem-n-tɑɑr ne bũmb ninsã."
  30,41,"Sãang pukɑ yɩng tẽn-gãng zug la Mogrẽ tɩ yɑɑ nebã nus sẽn tʋmã biisi, bʋl yĩng lɑ Wẽnd lemb-b b sẽn tʋmã sãnda tɩ sãn-sãnde b nɑ tek n bɑse."
  30,42,"Yeele: kẽn-y tẽmsã pʋsẽ n ges sẽn deng-b yãmb toaarã bɑɑsg yɩɩ wãn-wãnã? b sẽn yɩɩd wʋsg fãɑ yɩɩ lɑgem-n-tɑɑr rãmbɑ."
  30,43,"Bɩ f tees f nengã dĩin tɩrgẽ wã tɑoor tɩ rɑɑr sẽn ka tɑr lεbsdgã nɑn kɑ tɑ ye, bɑrɑɑr lɑ b nɑ n weel tɑɑbɑ."
  30,44,"Neb ning sẽn kɩfl-a, a kɩflg bee ne-a; lɑ neb nins sẽn tʋm sõama me yɑa b mens lɑ b segend n bĩngdẽ."
  30,45,"Bʋɩl yĩng lɑ A rol neb nins sẽn kõ-b sɩd lɑ b tʋm tʋʋm-sõmsã ne A yɩɩdlmã, ad A kɑ nong sõm-zɩtb ye."
  30,46,"Lɑ sẽn yi A yel-soɑlmã pʋgẽ yɑa ɑ sẽn tʋm sobdã tɩ b yɑɑ sũ-noogdba, bʋɩl yĩng tɩ y na lemb A yolsgã, lɑ bʋɩl yĩng tɩ koglsã kẽn ne A sɑgelle, lɑ bʋɩl yĩng tɩ y na bɑo A yɩɩdlmẽ wã, lɑ sãnd-sãnde y nɑ pʋʋs barka."
  30,47,"Sɩdɑ Tõnd tʋmɑ tẽn-tʋʋmb b nebã nengẽ toɑɑr tɩ fo nɑn kɑ wɑ. B wɑa b nengẽ ne vẽenem tɩ Tõnd sɩbg neb nins sẽn tʋmd yel-wẽnɑ; lɑ sɩd-kõɑtbã sõngr yɑɑ tɩlɑe ne Tõndo."
  30,48,"Wẽnd n tʋmd sobdã tɩ b peegd sɑwɑtã t'A sãeegd-b sɑɑsẽ wã wɑlɑ A sẽn dɑte, lɑ A mɑɑn tɩ b lebg sɑwɑd-pεl tɩ fo yẽt sɑ-koomã t'ɑ yit b pʋsẽ. A sã n sik-ɑ A sẽn dɑt-b rãmb A yembsã zugu, lɑ bãmb sẽn noogd b sũyã."
  30,49,"Lɑ tɑoor tɩ b nɑn kɑ sik-ɑ n kõ-ba, b ra yɩɩme n da wãag b tẽebo."
  30,50,"Bɩ f ges Wẽnd yolsgã vũunã A sẽn vʋʋgd tẽngã ɑ kũum poorã, ad yaa Yẽnda n vʋʋgd kiidba, la A yɑɑ bũmb fãɑ gill tõogda."
  30,51,"Lɑ tɩ Tõnd sã n tʋm sobg tɩ b yã-ɑ t'ɑ yɑɑ rõodo, b nɑ kell n pɑ ɑ loogr poorã n kɩfendẽ."
  30,52,"Rẽnd fo kɑ tõe n wʋmsg kũ-rãmb ye, lɑ fo kɑ tõe n wʋmsg wʋms boɑɑl tɩ b sã n gũd n teesdẽ ye."
  30,53,"Lɑ fo kɑ tõe n kãndg zoees n yiis b menengẽ wã ye; fo sẽn tõe n wʋms-b rãmb yaa neb nins sẽn kõ sɩd ne Tõnd goɑmã, bãmb rãmbɑ yaa sak-n-tũ rãmbɑ."
  30,54,"Wẽnd lɑ sẽn nɑɑn yãmb ne ko vɑlenga, rẽ poorẽ t'A kõ pãng vɑlengã loogr poore, rẽ poorẽ t'A kõ komsg lɑ kʋʋlem pãngã poore. A nɑɑndɑ A sẽn dɑte, lɑ Yẽnda lɑ bãngd lɑ tõog Naaba."
  30,55,"Lɑ raar ning dũni wã sẽn na n wa yikã, yel-wẽn-mɑɑndbã nɑ n wẽendɑme tɩ bãmb kɑ zĩnd rẽndɑ sɑsɑ-yεng bɑlɑ, yɑɑ woto lɑ b rɑg n wẽnesd-b dũni wã n yit sɩdã."
  30,56,"Lɑ b sẽn kõ-b rãmb bãngrã lɑ sɩd kũunã yeel-yã: ""sɩdɑ ɑd Wẽnd Sebrã pʋgẽ, yãmb pɑɑme hɑl n tãɑg Yikr rɑɑrã, rẽnd Yikr rɑɑrã lɑ woto, lɑ bũmb ning sẽn be yɑɑ tɩ yãmb rɑ yɩɩme n kɑ miẽ ye."
  30,57,"Rẽnd bɑrɑɑrã wẽgdbã pɑdengã kɑ nɑ n tɑll yõod ne-b ye, lɑ b kɑ nɑ n kõ-b sor me tɩ b bao lebgr ye."
  30,58,"La sɩd la hakɩɩka Tõnd rɩka Alkʋrãan-kãngã pʋgẽ bilgr buud toor-toore, la tɩ fo sã n wa ne Aayar n kõ-ba, kɩfr-rãmbã na yeele: ""ad yãmb yaa zĩrimbe-neb bala""."
  30,59,"Yɑɑ woto bɑl lɑ Wẽnd pɑgd sẽn kɑ mi-bã sũy wã."
  30,60,"Bɩ f mɑɑn sʋgri, bɑlɑ Wẽnd pʋlengã yɑa sɩdɑ, lɑ sẽn kɑ mɑɑnd-b bãng-n-wãɑkã rɑ wɑ tus foom tɩ f mɑɑn sũ-yikr ye."
